node.text: Spent a day baking with @bobsredmill in my home and in my studio. Celebrating the nurturing power of cooking for ourselves and others. Enter giveaway by visiting the link on my profile. #bobsbythebook #betterwithbobs

100 gluten and dairy-free baking recipes from breads such as baguettes, bagels, sourdough English muffins, cakes, cookies, tarts, holiday treats and more. Many plant-based options, always trying to incorporate classic techniques with modern and alternative ideas and flours.

More of what is inside the book on Stories.
